	<h1 class="title entry-title"><a rel="bookmark" href="http://scienceblogs.com/startswithabang/2013/04/05/long-for-the-stars/">Long for the Stars</a></h1>
	<div class="byline vcard author">
		
		<img alt='' src="http://scienceblogs.com/startswithabang/files/2013/10/SWAB_logo-58x58.jpg" class='avatar avatar-58 photo' height='58' width='58' />Posted by <span class="fn"><a href="http://scienceblogs.com/startswithabang/author/esiegel/" title="Posts by Ethan">Ethan</a></span> on <abbr class="published" title="2013-04-05T17:49:09+00:00">April 5, 2013</abbr> 	</div><!--/byline-->
</div><!--/header-->


<div class="box-share">
